    <newsTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Stories That Teach Real-Life Lessons]]></Value>
    </newsTitle>
    <newsExcerpt>
      <Value><![CDATA[Every Moo Family adventure carries a lesson — kindness, courage, curiosity, and creativity.]]></Value>
    </newsExcerpt>
    <newsBody>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Kids absorb lessons best through stories that feel like play. That's why every Moo Family episode is built around a values-driven moment.</p><p>New chapters added monthly cover responsibility, friendship, problem solving, and emotional awareness.</p>]]></Value>
